cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modeling and syntax-sensitive generalizations. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the inner mechanics of LSTMs. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as LSTMs are a popular tool in AI research. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks, and cs.SD (Sound) as it discusses the encoding of grammatical structure in language models.
